    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details>
        <summary>How long does delivery take?</summary>
        <p>Delivery time depends on the restaurant and your location — typically 25–45 minutes. During busy hours it may take longer.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
        <p>We accept credit/debit cards, major digital wallets, and cash on delivery where available.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Are there offers or discounts?</summary>
        <p>Yes — we run periodic promotions and partner discounts. Check the homepage banners or your account offers.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>What is your refund policy?</summary>
        <p>If an order is incorrect or missing items, contact us within 24 hours and we'll resolve it with a refund or replacement on a case-by-case basis.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Can I schedule an order for later?</summary>
        <p>Currently we support immediate orders; scheduled ordering is coming soon.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
